question: What restaurant can I find along the way to Go Fish, Rosedale, MD within 160 kilometers from River Deck, Edgewater, MD?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.540922 38.941815)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.48474 39.339761)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.540922 38.941815)',4326)::geography, 160000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.540922 38.941815)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
